Package pl.put.poznan.builder.logic

Class Element

  • java.lang.Object
    • pl.put.poznan.builder.logic.Element
  • public class Element
extends Object
    This class offers fine-grained control over the HTML tree. It is responsible for setting of all the details of a generic element.
